    "body": "When trying to install M4 with PGI, I ran into a problem. `make` would crash and `spack-build.out` would contain dozens of lines like:\n\n```\nbuiltin.o: In function `xnmalloc':\n/tmp/ajstewart/spack-stage/spack-stage-Mus3U5/m4-1.4.17/src/../lib/xalloc.h:104: multiple definition of `xnmalloc'\nm4.o:/tmp/ajstewart/spack-stage/spack-stage-Mus3U5/m4-1.4.17/src/../lib/xalloc.h:104: first defined here\n```\n\nAfter submitting a [bug report](http://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/bug-gnulib/2016-03/msg00006.html) with the developers of M4, they provided me with this patch to get things working.\n",
